    public class SystemProjectionRepository<I,P extends Projection<I,S,?>,S extends com.google.protobuf.Message>
extends ProjectionRepository<I,P,S>
    A repository for projections in a system bounded context.

    Unlike an arbitrary ProjectionRepository, a SystemProjectionRepository dispatches the events directly to the target projections.

      • dispatchTo

        protected void dispatchTo(I id,
                          io.spine.core.Event event)
        Dispatches the given event to an entity with the given ID.

        Sends a system command to dispatch the given event to a subscriber.

        Overrides:
        dispatchTo in class ProjectionRepository<I,P extends Projection<I,S,?>,S extends com.google.protobuf.Message>
        Parameters:
        id - the target entity ID
        event - the event to dispatch
        Implementation Note:
        A SystemProjectionRepository dispatches the given event directly to its targets, whereas a domain repository would send a command to the system context.
